{"tid":2145595,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：政府在6月中放寬多項防疫措施，是很大的錯誤","createTime":"2020-08-08T06:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T07:39:39.000Z","uid":212626,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"464a2674cae58cb801b96cf3d295a8f94a308a53","tid":2145595,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"政府專家顧問、香港大學微生物學系講座教授袁國勇在本台節目表示，本港第三波疫情已有2800多人確診，主要是本地個案，認為新一輪疫情是由豁免檢測安排引致，加上放寬了防疫措施，市民開始鬆懈。他指，政府在6月中放寬多項防疫措施，是很大的錯誤，反映對疫症認識不足，強調病毒傳染性非常高，除非有相當針對性的措施，確保能控制高危群組傳播，加上有足夠的病毒檢測，否則不可以隨意放鬆防疫措施。 <br />\n<br />\n袁國勇又說，今波疫情在上月17日開始接近高峰，現在開始下降，證明收緊防疫措施開始有成效，但由於測試數目不足，而且社區仍有隱形傳播鏈，預料在一段時間內，每日都會有80多宗確診個案。 市民採樣方式不正確會影響檢測效果 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2351251&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDBq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=00f33f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351251</a>"},{"pid":"e25a338e03349c2e365023b753802e7396e7a4a0","tid":2145595,"uid":137344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"絕對認同<br />\n【正視聽】第三波疫情爆發係來自「因香港特別行政區政府鬆弛有道可防可控的防疫措施所造成的漏洞的豁免檢疫人士」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fMyFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fMyFcS</a>"},{"pid":"6df7b5413c05a0b07f07d261ac214663aba0dcc9","tid":2145595,"uid":171849,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:35:29.000Z","msg":"聽日準備收回言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a3a63a45e5db87e655b87b2af0dd28d893c51e","tid":2145595,"uid":93600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"rt&lt;1係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ddf082f0adb5f1114f4a02b31737bc9c2471eb","tid":2145595,"uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"市民採樣方式不正確會影響檢測效果 政府即將推出「普及社區檢測計劃」，袁國勇認為是好政策，指無論採集甚麼樣本，包括咽拭子或深喉唾液樣本都無問題，但強調採樣方法一定要正確，否則會影響樣本質素。 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">他舉例說，採集咽喉拭子樣本，要在喉嚨近扁桃腺的位置取樣才有用，鼻咽拭子亦要深入至近耳朵位置，才算有效</span>；如果做得不好，即使採樣採到流鼻血或嘔吐，樣本質素都很差。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2351251&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDBq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=00f33f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351251</a><br />\n柒婆叫人自己撩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5ead6386712b38d230c813390bb1c1f937b0d1","tid":2145595,"uid":278168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6df7b5413c05a0b07f07d261ac214663aba0dcc9","tid":2145595,"uid":171849,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:35:29.000Z","msg":"聽日準備收回言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:37:57.000Z","msg":"不嬲要收回嘅都係真話"},{"pid":"c5c01dc5f099dad8d719b08a233375ddb2e56be2","tid":2145595,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6df7b5413c05a0b07f07d261ac214663aba0dcc9","tid":2145595,"uid":171849,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:35:29.000Z","msg":"聽日準備收回言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b017db9eed87462105b356b6b1a305e719806e2","tid":2145595,"uid":266336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xD1TAAO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxD1TAAO.gif&h=97a91c88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8373248b87847f1d6925e04c024b3004e6111df6","tid":2145595,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6df7b5413c05a0b07f07d261ac2146